Package org.neo4j.tooling.procedure.validators

Class AllowedTypesValidator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.tooling.procedure.validators.AllowedTypesValidator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Predicate<TypeMirror>
    public class AllowedTypesValidator
extends Object
implements Predicate<TypeMirror>
    This predicate makes sure that a given declared type (record field type, procedure parameter type...) is supported by Neo4j stored procedures.
